CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 24, 1962, pg. A1 reads: "Left to right, Darline Grimmett, John Brewer, principal of Miller Elementary School and Priscilla Thompson."
TitMainTitle: Principal John Brewer Sr. holding hands of Darline Grimmett and Priscilla Thompson, walking out of Miller Elementary School into snow
